title: Fonkin "Badger" Murnig
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Fonkin "Badger" Murnig is a male gnome, recognizable for his exceptional beauty. He has high Constitution and low Strength. He has a talent: he is great with children. He tends to pace and is curious in his dealings with others.

He is dedicated to fulfilling a personal life goal and protective of a valuable possession. If you asked him, he would say that his Ideal is, "Redemption!" If he has a flaw, it is that he has a specific phobia.